All Classes

  • All Classes Interface Summary Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AlienAttacker
    A wrapper for the attacking algorithm interface.
    AlienAttackerFactory
    A factory for creating the AlienAttacker class instances.
    AlienNameGenerator
    This class is responsible for generating alien race names.
    AlienRace
    A class for representing an alien race in the simulation.
    AlienRaceAttackingAlgo
    An interface for creating algorithms to determine the win condition of a war between two races on a solar system.
    AlienRaceTrader
    A class that takes care of the trading done between races while visiting.
    AlienRelationship
    A class representing a relationship of two alien races.
    AlienRelationships
    A class representing a relationship of every alien race.
    Application
    Class Application is the main class.
    ApplicationProperties
    The class holds given arguments - variables used to run the simulation.
    ArgumentHandler
    This class is used to combine the two Maps of String value data, parse them and return data in form of ArgumentProperties object.
    ConsoleConfiguration
    The class is used to take the arguments array and return a Map of them for further operations on it.
    DataToCsvWriter
    This class is being used to write data lines to an output.csv file.
    Galaxy
    A class in which the whole simulation is happening.
    GalaxyCreator
    A class for creating and initializing a galaxy class.
    GalaxyField
    A class that represents a field in the galaxy's grid.
    GalaxyPrinter
    A class that prints the state of the aliens occupying a given galaxy.
    IConsoleConfiguration  
    IJsonConfiguration  
    JsonConfiguration
    This class reads the configuration file and returns them as a HashMap.
    MoneyAlienRaceAttackingAlgo
    Check who should win the war by checking who has more money.
    MotherShip
    A class that represents a mother ship in the simulation.
    MotherShipMover
    Class with methods for moving the mother ship.
    NeighbourAlienRaceAttackingAlgo
    Check who should win the war by checking who has its own other solar system closer to the attacked solar system.
    RandomAlienRaceAttackingAlgo
    Check who should win the war randomly.
    SaveGenerationData
    This class serves to prepare the csv file and extract data from Galaxy class.
    SolarSystem
    Class for simulating the solar systems.
    SolarSystemVisitor
    Class for visiting a solar system by a mother ship.
